{"tid":2208091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★又升！PS5日本炒到37000港元  Sony官方回應：「請停止相關行為」","createTime":"2020-09-18T15:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T05:31:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e8cdd0101ab74008d3028a73ad53d278dc2eb6","tid":2208091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"Sony Interactive Entertainment（SIE）在數日前終於公布新世代遊戲主機 PlayStation 5（PS5）的售價，並表示將於 11 月 12 日起正式發貨，目前各大購物平台已開放預購。不過，日本 Amazon 卻有商家在買家進行預訂後，偷偷將定價提升，最誇張可高達 500,000 日元，而若取消訂購亦將會收取 50,000 日元（約港幣 HKD$3688）的騷擾費，令不少日本網民紛紛在社交網路上表示不滿，並在 Twitter 發起行動反對。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據 Sony 的官方定價，光碟版 PS5 的未含稅價格為 49,980 日元（約港幣 HKD$3688），香港官方建議售價則為 HKD$3980。不過，目前在日本 Amazon 搜索 PS5，會出現為數不少將定價設於 350,000 日元（約港幣 HKD$25,820）或以上的商品，該些出售網點多是由 Amazon 許可的 &ldquo;Amazon Marketplace&rdquo; 註冊供應商，當中更有部份商家標價 500,000 日元（約港幣 HKD$36,888），且警告若取消訂購將會收取 50,000 日元（約港幣 HKD$3688）的騷擾費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據指，該批高額預訂價是依照官方訂價之後再加多一個「0」，即由原本的 35,800 日元變成 358,000 日元 (原價 10 倍價格)，誘騙買家下單。亦有賣家聲言無法免費取消訂購，故引起大批日本網民不滿，在 Twitter 上發起了大規模的聲討，並呼籲大家盡量將消息散播開去，以免有更多的受害者出現。大部份買家在其後表示，向 Amazon 反映相關事件後，最終成功免費取消訂單，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/09/18/500000yen-ps5/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F18%2F500000yen-ps5%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=970743f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/09/18/500000yen-ps5/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"131fff269c474b50686a8362da06590d9d3a30b1","tid":2208091,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"勁過bitcoin"},{"pid":"042114d10e55d148615b86fe7beeae2d3a0f693f","tid":2208091,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"131fff269c474b50686a8362da06590d9d3a30b1","tid":2208091,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"勁過bitcoin"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e0cf5f67d2bd9d94acdeaac5b91434a260c1a1","tid":2208091,"uid":151074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmdMwdY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmdMwdY.jpg&h=fa38b246&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7360f02dc37b81aacfa0d8973840c75a5ef47f36","tid":2208091,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"砌到部行3090加個4k moon"},{"pid":"a2667eb3c498e31bf6245f20c7fd12ecee5af5b4","tid":2208091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4af329ff16b2d2e03d26b364f7b848fc7aa9c6cc","tid":2208091,"uid":346404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:31:23.000Z","msg":"你炒價還炒價。但加個0搏好彩厄人係仆街，仲要set如果人地撳錯要收一部機價錢既手續費。定係amazon俾人咁做？"}]}